Installation of GIT
=====================

check whether java is installed or not

yum install curl curl-devel

yum groupinstall "Development Tools"

yum install gettext-devel openssl-devel perl-CPAN perl-devel zlib-devel

go to github page and download latest git source code

https://github.com/git/git/releases

wget link

mv v2.12.0-rc0.tar.gz to /opt/software/.

rename the v2.12.0-rc0.tar.gz to git-2.12.tar.gz

untar it using the command

tar -xzf git-2.12.tar.gz

cd git-*

make configure

./configure --prefix=/usr/local

 make install


git --version


git config --global user.name "your Name"
git config --global user.mail "you@example.com"


git config --list

